  <description><![CDATA[<h2>Explore Italy's largest lake and the diverse history, activities and culture it has to offer on this multi-centre holiday.</h2>
<p>A multi-centre holiday to <a data-udi="umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473}" title="Lake Garda">Lake Garda</a> means you get to experience the best of the North and the South of the lake. Spend a couple of days walking past historic castles and rustic towns in Sirmione or Garda, before heading North for a more active side to the lake, from paddle boarding in Riva, to walking on Monte Baldo in Malcesine. We have two combinations available, these are <a data-udi="umb://document/689f022eb7974a7087ccbecf4adbda43" href="/{localLink:umb://document/689f022eb7974a7087ccbecf4adbda43}" title="Garda">Garda</a> &amp; <a data-udi="umb://document/8bac09b5ee37405a9498e1494235fa01" href="/{localLink:umb://document/8bac09b5ee37405a9498e1494235fa01}" title="Riva">Riva</a> and <a data-udi="umb://document/93a0ea3cd0334ca088eaf788bad0faba" href="/{localLink:umb://document/93a0ea3cd0334ca088eaf788bad0faba}" title="Sirmione">Sirmione</a> &amp; <a data-udi="umb://document/89a5238595c34e53a5ef4c989b459fce" href="/{localLink:umb://document/89a5238595c34e53a5ef4c989b459fce}" title="Malcesine">Malcesine</a>.</p>
<h3>Your multi-centre holiday options:</h3>
<ul>
<ul>
<li>7, 11 or 14 nights accommodation in your chosen hotels</li>
<li>Travel on Wednesday or Saturday</li>
</ul>
</ul>
<h3>Your holiday includes:</h3>
<ul>
<ul>
<li>Return flights from the UK</li>
<li>Return airport transfers (direct) to and from your chosen hotels</li>
<li>Up to two guided walks per person per week if staying in Garda</li>
</ul>
</ul>
