  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<h2>Hotels in Sirmione &amp; Malcesine</h2>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/546df43cd8254f9eaecd12ec05609999" href="/{localLink:umb://document/546df43cd8254f9eaecd12ec05609999}" title="Hotel Sirmione">Hotel Sirmione, Sirmione</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 320px; height: 220px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13078353/hotel-sirmione.jpg?width=500&amp;height=268.49642004773267" alt="hotel sirmione" data-udi="umb://media/65fffb3d57a948ab90b929a3a6ab82b4" />Hotel Sirmione's in the centre of the resort and right on the edge of the lake. It's known for its spa and has a great indoor thermal pool. Head outside and take in the stunning lake views from the lakeside terrace which is the perfect place for an Aperol Spritz!</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/7988d4b67ae9445e8ee106e20f92c80e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7988d4b67ae9445e8ee106e20f92c80e}" title="Hotel Catullo">Hotel Catullo, Sirmione</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 320px; height: 220px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13090907/from-catullo-with-love.jpg?width=500&amp;height=268.49642004773267" alt="catullo" data-udi="umb://media/fe10f0768edc4609819bb085e7153557" /></p>
<p>Hotel Catullo is located in Sirmione's colourful pedestrianised centre right on the lakefront. The hotel's lakeside terrace is one of the best places to watch the sunset in Sirmione. It's an easy walk from the ferry port and a longstanding favourite of ours.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/e647d3120e5c40fa8c337a86bfee1937" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e647d3120e5c40fa8c337a86bfee1937}" title="Hotel Majestic Palace">Hotel Majestic Palace, Malcesine</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 320px; height: 220px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13089954/dji_0002.jpg?width=500&amp;height=268.49642004773267" alt="Majestic palace" data-udi="umb://media/7f7551907ed841f4b63aeba49eb91ca7" /></p>
<p>The Hotel Majestic Palace is a great place for an action-packed family holiday. With four swimming pools, tennis, mini-golf and more you'll have everything you need right on your doorstep.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473}" title="Lake Garda" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn c-btn--mid c-btn--secondary-hollow c-btn--wide u-text-center">View all Hotels in Lake Garda</a></p>
<p><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call Us to Book Today</a></p>]]></facilityDescription>
  <familyDescription><![CDATA[<h2>Hotels in Garda &amp; Riva</h2>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/c85ff8ee0bc44bee8157ff1b59821c85" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c85ff8ee0bc44bee8157ff1b59821c85}" title="Hotel Bisesti">Hotel Bisesti, Garda</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 320px; height: 220px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13071987/hotel-bisesti-garda-pool-night.jpg?width=500&amp;height=268.49642004773267" alt="bisesti" data-udi="umb://media/975c7d0cb3ab4cb9b4a31389da87f07d" /></p>
<p>Hotel Bisesti is a family-run hotel that's full of charm. It's got a great restaurant and a large pool with lot's of space for soaking up the summer sun. It's close to the centre of Garda, and the lakefront promenade's just a short walk from the hotel.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/582c1440c43347c6a27756575d766e8e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/582c1440c43347c6a27756575d766e8e}" title="Hotel Garden">Hotel Garden, Garda</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 320px; height: 220px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13089991/garden.jpg?width=500&amp;height=268.49642004773267" alt="garden" data-udi="umb://media/6814360e88f04ac5bbb1631ece203016" /></p>
<p>Hotel Garden is next to Garda's bustling lakefront promenade yet still manages to feel secluded. It's got large, peaceful gardens where you'll find a pool with lake views. The gardens are the perfect place to relax on your summer holiday.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/3566c3c4f3024dac8793ab30719f7066" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3566c3c4f3024dac8793ab30719f7066}" title="Hotel Du Lac Et Du Parc">Hotel du Lac et du Parc, Riva</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 320px; height: 220px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13074587/du-lac-et-du-parc-hotel-gardens.jpg?width=500&amp;height=268.49642004773267" alt="du lac et du parc" data-udi="umb://media/8071f2a07ec849dba29a3ed50cee2995" /></p>
<p>Hotel Du Lac et Du Parc has something for everyone. If you want to relax there's the beautiful park with winding pathways that lead down to the lakefront and an excellent spa.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473}" title="Lake Garda" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn c-btn--mid c-btn--secondary-hollow c-btn--wide u-text-center">View all Hotels in Lake Garda</a></p>
<p><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call Us to Book Today</a></p>]]></familyDescription>
