  <locationDescription><![CDATA[<div class="c-page-content">
<p>A multi-centre holiday lets you mix and match hotels, lengths of stay, and exciting activities to create your ideal trip. Enjoy everything from guided walks and outdoor adventures to relaxing lakeside days and tasty local cuisine.</p>
<p><strong>Explore Sirmione &amp; Malcesine</strong></p>
<p>Sirmione and Malcesine are a match made in heaven for history and culture lovers alike. In both resorts you'll find a Scaligero castle, a symbol of the historic La Scala family dynasty in the Veneto region. With easily accessible ferry points these are both great bases for exploring other towns on Lake Garda during your holiday. Come back in the evenings to lakeside views and an Aperol or limoncello spritz in hand! Sirmione is known for it's old cobbled streets and having the best gelato on Lake Garda, and Malcesine for Monte Baldo which is a great place for walking, head up on the cable car for panoramic views of the lake.</p>
<p><strong>Relax in Garda &amp; Riva</strong></p>
<p>Get to know the North and South of the Lake Garda and all the exciting opportunities for getting out and about. Walk around Garda in the South and explore the shops, grab a gelato by the lakeside or head off on one of our included guided walks. Take in the views from the top of La Rocca or head out with the family to the nearby Gardaland theme park. Riva, in the North, is a fantastic place for watersports enthusiasts; with beaches, paddle boarding, windsurfing and more! You could spend a day walking along the Ponale Way from Riva to <a data-udi="umb://document/ee16f6b7f5224e5c8d9b68f1d4b62c0b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ee16f6b7f5224e5c8d9b68f1d4b62c0b}" title="Lake Ledro">Lake Ledro</a>, admiring the lake views or visit the Varone waterfall and caves, walking through the botanical gardens around it. This is a great multi-centre for families, full of entertainment for all ages!</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473}" title="Lake Garda" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn c-btn--mid c-btn--secondary-hollow c-btn--wide u-text-center">Find Out More About Lake Garda</a></p>
<p><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call Us to Book Today</a></p>
</div>]]></locationDescription>
